1
00:00:00,000 --> 00:00:04,400
Science has a clearer story about monsoons than social media does.

2
00:00:04,400 --> 00:00:08,000
Monsoons occur when land heats up faster than oceans.

3
00:00:08,000 --> 00:00:09,600
This creates pressure differences.

4
00:00:09,600 --> 00:00:14,800
As warm air rises, it pulls in moisture-laden winds, leading to heavy rains.

5
00:00:14,800 --> 00:00:21,200
These rains are crucial for agriculture in many regions, but they can also cause devastating floods.

6
00:00:21,200 --> 00:00:26,400
So, next time you hear about monsoons, remember, there’s science behind the storms.

7
00:00:26,400 --> 00:00:28,400
